snippet.title: Hassle 1977 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Break into the Baltic City and join the resistance force Free Breath! Show and prove your skills in PvP shootouts, PvE missions, online drift and street races among other players-rebels and earn respect among them!

Hassle 1977 is a cross-platform game for PC, consoles and mobiles.

PC: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1218550/Hassle_1977/
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/ru/app/hassle-1977/id1493945880?l=en
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.limkernel.hassle1977
PS4: coming soon
XboxOne: coming soon
Nintendo Switch: coming soon
